<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="18Mar1938"><font color="red">18 March 1938</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from T.S. Eliot to Paul L&eacute;on): Thank you for your letter of the 16th. I &hellip; pass it on to Mr de la Mare &hellip; I am sorry to hear of the cause of the interruption of Mr Joyce&apos;s work &hellip; I am very glad to hear that his work has been progressing so well. </div>
